IProxySerialization
public class GwtProxySerialization
extends GwtSerializer
implements IProxySerialization

GWT compatible map serialization. Each basic type is encapsulated as IRequestParameter. Non basic type is serialised as string and send as this

Author:
bruno.marchesson
